title: TNF Preview, Week 6 WR/CB Matchups 2022
description:
Field Yates and Daniel Dopp preview Thursday Night Football before dishing out the WR’s who have great matchups and the WR’s who you may need to bench. Then, Adam Schefter joins to talk the storylines to watch in Week 6 including what to make of some tough matchups and preview some key games for the Sunday.
